{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/layouts"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some components can be used for "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"layouts"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"title":"Layouts","role":"article","roleHeading":"Article"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Layouts","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Colored-Surface","text":"Colored Surface"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Colored backgrounds use surface colors to maximize the contrast with content."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The colors of several OUDS components (for instance "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":") are automatically adjusted if they are placed on "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSColoredSurface","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do so, some tokens associated with these specific colors can be customized and are identified with the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Mono","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" suffix (for instance "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"buttonColorBgDefaultEnabledMono"}]},{"type":"text","text":" of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"How-it-works","text":"How it works"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the color, the "},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" component adds in SwiftUI environment two flags:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"oudsUseMonochrome","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": to inform a component that needs to use mono version of tokens"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"oudsOnColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": to inform a component it is placed on colored surface even if the mono is off"}]}]}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"How-to-use","text":"How to use"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ The folowing view has a colored background \"modeOnStatusPositiveEmphasized\" with","    \/\/ - a text with the color adapted according to the adjusted colorScheme      ","    \/\/ - a button that uses the mono version of tokens","","    \/\/ As view","    OUDSColoredSurface(color: theme.colorModes.modeOnStatusPositiveEmphasized) {","        VStack {","            Text(\"Status Positive Emphasized\")","            .oudsForegroundColor(theme.colors.colorContentDefault)","","            OUDSButton(text: \"Button\") {}","        }","    }","","    \/\/ As view modifier","","    VStack {","        Text(\"Status Positive Emphasized\")","        .oudsForegroundColor(theme.colors.colorContentDefault)","","        OUDSButton(text: \"Button\") {}","    }","    .oudsColoredSurface(theme.colorModes.modeOnStatusPositiveEmphasized)"]},{"level":5,"type":"heading","anchor":"Debuging-contrast-ratios","text":"Debuging contrast ratios"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr\/"},{"type":"text","text":", also named “RGAA”."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However it is highly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for texts and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Some components like ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be used on ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSColoredSurface","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ; thus in that case we can know the surface color for a given component on it, and compute the contrast ratio, and in the end display or not warnings.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To do that, some steps must be followed in your component implementation:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rise the flag to allow debugging (e.g. i #DEBUG mode)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Get the environement variable defined by the colored surface containing the applied color","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the component implementation, add a line of code comparing the color to test and that surface"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then keep an eye on your logs ; warnings will be added there if WCAG 2.1 3:1, 4.5:1 or 7:1 ratios are not reached, depending to the methods you call","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Rise the flag","#if DEBUG","OUDSWCAG21Ratios.oudsDebugWCAG21Colors = true","#endif","","\/\/ Supposing we are in your component View \/ ViewModifer struct","","\/\/ Get the applied surface color","@Environment(\\.oudsSurfaceColor) var surfaceColor","","\/\/ In the function defining the color to apply, add the line below","\/\/ where colorTokenToApply is the color to apply from a theme:","","\/\/ Non-textual components, in AA","OUDSWCAG21Ratios.debugContrastRatio(colorToApply, surfaceColor, .nonTextual)","","\/\/ Textual components and AAA to check","OUDSWCAG21Ratios.debugContrastRatio(colorToApply, surfaceColor, .AAA)"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Divider","text":"Divider"},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"How-it-works","text":"How it works"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A divider is used to separate content elements in a view. Two kinds of divider are proposed:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" To separate elements stacked vertivally (VStask).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSVerticalDivider"},{"type":"text","text":" To separate elements stacked Horizontally (HStask)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A divider can be colored using color enumerated in the "},{"code":"OUDSDividerColor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"How-to-use","text":"How to use"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Add a vertical divider between items","HStack {","    Text(\"Hello wolrd!\")","    OUDSVerticalDivider(color: .brandPrimary)","    Text(\"Happy to see you\")","}","","\/\/ Add an horizontal divider between items","VStack {","    Text(\"Hello wolrd!\")","    OUDSHorizontalDivider(color: .brandPrimary)","    Text(\"Happy to see you\")","}"]}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSButton":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSButton","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSButton","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbutton","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only, icon only or text with icon."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSButton","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSComponents","abstract":[{"text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" extensions and ","type":"text"},{"code":"ViewModifiers","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSLink":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudslink","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSLink"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSLink"}],"title":"OUDSLink","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only or text with icon."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It also proposes layout to navigate forward or backward. The link can be displayed in "},{"code":"small","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"default","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" size."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSColoredSurface":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSColoredSurface","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscoloredsurface","abstract":[{"text":"Used to define if a content is used on a colored surface.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSColoredSurface","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSColoredSurface","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSColoredSurface"},"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr/":{"title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr\/","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr\/"}}}